Company Overview of Granite Investment Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Granite Investment Partners, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also provides its services to individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations and other businesses, and state and municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalizations to create its equity portfolios. It benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against various Russell indices. Th...
Granite Investment Partners, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm primarily provides its services to high net worth individuals. It also provides its services to individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations and other businesses, and state and municipal government entities. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It invests in the public equity markets across the globe. The firm invests in growth and value stocks of companies across diversified market capitalizations to create its equity portfolios. It benchmarks the performance of its equity portfolios against various Russell indices. The firm employs fundamental analysis with focus on bottom up approach to make its investments. It employs a combination of external and in-house research to manage its portfolio. Granite Investment Partners, LLC was founded in July 2009 and is based in El Segundo, California.
